# Coding Rules

Structure

Max 3 levels deep
Linear flow: input → process → output
Group related data together

Responsibility

One function = one job
Max 5 methods per interface
No code duplication

Clarity

Explicit dependencies as parameters
Simple solutions over clever code
Only implement what's needed now

Quick Check

✓ Max 3 levels
✓ Linear flow
✓ Single responsibility
✓ Explicit deps
